<h4>6. List an envelope's documents</h4>
<p>List the envelope's documents. A <i>Certificate of Completion</i> document
    is also associated with every envelope.
</p>

<p>This method is often used to dynamically create a list of an envelope's documents
    in preparation for enabling your user to download one or more of the documents.</p>

<% if (showDoc) { %>
    <p><a target='_blank' href='<%= documentation %>'>Documentation</a> about this example.</p>
<% } %>

<p>API method used:
    <a target='_blank' href="https://developers.docusign.com/esign-rest-api/reference/Envelopes/EnvelopeDocuments/list">EnvelopeDocuments::list</a>.
</p>

<% include ../../partials/gitSource %>
<% if (envelopeOk) { %>
    <p>The envelope you created via example 2 will be queried.</p>

    <form class="eg" action="" method="post" data-busy="form">
        <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%- csrfToken %>">
        <input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Continue FormEnvOK</input>
    </form>

    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.6.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function() {
            window.document.forms[0].submit();
        });
    </script>

